<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>회원가입</h1>
        <form action="/register" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="id">아이디:</label>
                <input type="text" id="id" name="id" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="pw">비밀번호:</label>
                <input type="password" id="pw" name="pw" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="name">이름:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="sch_name">학교명:</label>
                <input type="text" id="sch_name" name="sch_name" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="sch_class">성별:</label>
                <input type="text" placeholder="여성 / 남성중 하나로 적어주세요" id="gender" name="gender" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="sch_class">나이:</label>
                <input type="text" id="age" name="age" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="sch_class">인스타그램:</label>
                <input type="text" id="instagram" name="instagram" required>
            </div>

            <button type="submit">가입하기</button>
        </form>
        <p>이미 계정이 있으신가요? <a href="/login">로그인</a></p>
        <p class="mini-text">비밀번호는 안전하게 암호화 됩니다</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>